Commands:
minibot <command> <value>
OR
mb <command> <value>

commands:
    no_congrats
        disables congrats messages
    yes_congrats
        enables congrats messages (enabled by default)
    no_leaderboard
        will leave you off the daily leaderboard
    yes_leaderboard (default)
        will put you back on the daily leaderboard
    no_rekkening
        will leave you off the rekkening
    yes_rekkening (default)
        will put you back on the rekkening
    goofy_ratio
        on a scale of 1-10, how often do you want to receive goofy messages, rather than the normal ones? Default: 0